title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Identify all parts supplied by suppliers located in Germany whose individual stock value exceeds 0.0001 of the total stock value of all German suppliers. The stock value of each part is defined as ps_supplycost * ps_availqty. Use only suppliers from the nation ‘GERMANY’, compute the total stock value for Germany, and return only those parts whose value is greater than 0.0001 of that total. Output in Textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT n_nationkey, n_name FROM nation) as n
(SELECT s_suppkey, s_nationkey FROM supplier) as s

operations.udf: (t: ((Integer, Integer), (Integer, Integer))) => { val ps_suppkey = t._1; val s_suppkey = t._2; (ps_suppkey, s_suppkey) }

operations.table: (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_suppkey, ps_supplycost, ps_availqty FROM partsupp) as ps

operations.udf: (t: ((Integer, Integer), (Integer, Integer))) => { val ps_partkey = t._1._1; val ps_supplycost = t._2._1; val ps_availqty = t._2._2; val stock = ps_supplycost * ps_availqty; (ps_partkey, stock) }
(t: ((Integer, Double), (Integer, Double))) => { val total = t._2._2; val stock = t._1._2; stock > 0.0001 * total }

log.thoughts: Identify German suppliers, compute each German stock value (ps_supplycost * ps_availqty), sum to get total German stock, and filter parts where individual stock exceeds 0.0001 of that total. Output the resulting part identifiers to a text file.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.udf: (t: ((Integer, Integer), (Integer, Integer))) => { val ps_suppkey = t._1; val s_suppkey = t._2; (ps_suppkey, s_suppkey) }

data.table: (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_suppkey, ps_supplycost, ps_availqty FROM (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_suppkey, ps_supplycost, ps_availqty FROM partsupp) as ps) as X

data.udf: (t: ((Integer, Integer), (Integer, Integer))) => { val ps_partkey = t._1._1; val ps_supplycost = t._2._1; val ps_availqty = t._2._2; val stock = ps_supplycost * ps_availqty; (ps_partkey, stock) }
(t: ((Integer, Double), (Integer, Double))) => { val total = t._2._2; val stock = t._1._2; stock > 0.0001 * total }
